name: Crit notes
description:
Little utilities for making your Figma experience even better. Get your copy and publish it as a library for your team to use in design critique and "whiteboarding" sessions.

Contents:
• Notes for critique sessions and feedback.
• Dot stickers for voting, remix of Jordan's "Dot Stickers" (figma.com/c/file/821860975331219068)
• Comments notice, for flagging the presence of comments.
